Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:08.84,English,,0,0,0,,there are two beings here okay we believe\N{\rChinese}这里有两位存在，好，我们认为
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:13.38,English,,0,0,0,,that these two beings represent the mother goddess\N{\rChinese}这两位存在代表母神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:17.68,English,,0,0,0,,because as we discussed last class the mother goddess comes in\N{\rChinese}因为正如我们上节讨论的，母神以鸟的形象出现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:23.62,English,,0,0,0,,the form of a bird right the bird flies around the sky the sky is the mother goddess okay\N{\rChinese}鸟在天空中飞翔，天空即是母神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.62,0:24:26.04,English,,0,0,0,,so it's almost like the mother goddess is\N{\rChinese}于是它几乎像母神在通道或驱动动物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.04,0:24:30.18,English,,0,0,0,,channeling or hurting the animals from a\N{\rChinese}从动物那里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.18,0:24:35.54,English,,0,0,0,,spirit world back into our own world what you also notice is\N{\rChinese}灵界回到我们自己的世界，你还会注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.54,0:24:40.52,English,,0,0,0,,that these birds almost like humans okay\N{\rChinese}这些鸟几乎像人类
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.52,0:24:42.56,English,,0,0,0,,and so we what we think is that\N{\rChinese}于是我们认为是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.56,0:24:47.04,English,,0,0,0,,the shamans dress up like birds\N{\rChinese}萨满们会化身成鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.04,0:24:52.12,English,,0,0,0,,in order to channel the energy of the mother goddess to control the animals okay Okay?\N{\rChinese}以此化身以通母神之能，控制动物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.18,0:24:55.40,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, and there's actually a lot of evidence for this.\N{\rChinese}好的，实际上有很多证据。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.94,0:25:01.90,English,,0,0,0,,So, this is clearly an animal,\N{\rChinese}所以，这明显是个动物，
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.76,0:25:06.76,English,,0,0,0,,but this is also a person who's an animal, who's a human being, right?\N{\rChinese}但这也是个动物的人，还是个人的存在，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.10,0:25:08.62,English,,0,0,0,,Because of the figure.\N{\rChinese}因为这个形象。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.82,0:25:11.22,English,,0,0,0,,So these are human beings, shamans, who\N{\rChinese}于是这些人是萨满，萨满们，
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.22,0:25:14.98,English,,0,0,0,,dress up like animals in order to better communicate with animals,\N{\rChinese}他们化身成动物，以更好地与动物沟通。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.16,0:25:22.70,English,,0,0,0,,but also to better communicate with the spirit world, okay? And\N{\rChinese}但也是为了更好地与灵界沟通，明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.70,0:25:28.12,English,,0,0,0,,this is actually a more clear picture of shamans trying to access the spirit world.\N{\rChinese}这实际上是萨满试图进入灵界的更清晰画面。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.48,0:25:34.38,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, are we clear so far?\N{\rChinese}好的，到此为止，我们明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.60,0:25:39.98,English,,0,0,0,,So, from this religion, we can guess\N{\rChinese}于是，从这宗教可以推测
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.98,0:25:44.26,English,,0,0,0,,that the people back then were extremely compassionate.\N{\rChinese}当时的人们极为仁慈
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.86,0:25:46.58,English,,0,0,0,,They believed that\N{\rChinese}他们相信
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.58,0:25:49.86,English,,0,0,0,,everything has a soul,\N{\rChinese}一切皆有灵魂，每一生命都珍贵。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.96,0:25:52.02,English,,0,0,0,,and every life is precious.\N{\rChinese}好的？而这就是一条证据。
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.04,0:25:55.28,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? And one evidence for this is this.\N{\rChinese}Okay? And one evidence for this is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.06,0:25:59.78,English,,0,0,0,,This is a skeleton.\N{\rChinese}这是一个骷髓。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.46,0:26:05.26,English,,0,0,0,,What's interesting about the skeleton is that it's a dwarf, okay?\N{\rChinese}这骷髓的有趣之处在于它是一个矮人，好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.84,0:26:08.94,English,,0,0,0,,So there are some humans back then who\N{\rChinese}于是，那时有些人类是这样……
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.94,0:26:12.84,English,,0,0,0,,are born with diseases, or handicaps,\N{\rChinese}出生时就有疾病，或残疾，或体形畸形。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.84,0:26:14.04,English,,0,0,0,,or physical deformities.\N{\rChinese}这人是个矮人。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.40,0:26:15.74,English,,0,0,0,,This person is a dwarf.\N{\rChinese}This person is adwarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.28,0:26:18.52,English,,0,0,0,,Now, this is interesting because\N{\rChinese}现在，这很有趣，因为……
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.52,0:26:22.02,English,,0,0,0,,dwarfs aren't able to communicate with humans.\N{\rChinese}矮人无法与人类交流。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.02,0:26:23.66,English,,0,0,0,,They're not able to contribute that much to your community, right?\N{\rChinese}他们也无法为你的社区做出太多贡献，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.92,0:26:25.44,English,,0,0,0,,So as a hunter -gatherer,\N{\rChinese}于是作为狩猎采集者，
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.58,0:26:28.48,English,,0,0,0,,you need to hunt together to access meat,\N{\rChinese}你需要一起狩猎才能获得肉类，
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.64,0:26:30.44,English,,0,0,0,,to get meat, to feed everyone.\N{\rChinese}以便给大家喂食。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.96,0:26:32.16,English,,0,0,0,,If you're a dwarf,\N{\rChinese}如果你是矮人，你也没什么大事做。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.60,0:26:34.96,English,,0,0,0,,you're not really doing that much.\N{\rChinese}于是理论上，因为……
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.62,0:26:38.52,English,,0,0,0,,So in theory, because\N{\rChinese}So in theory, because
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.52,0:26:41.54,English,,0,0,0,,it's such a harsh life,\N{\rChinese}是个艰难的生活，
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.90,0:26:46.04,English,,0,0,0,,being a hunter -gatherer, you would think that they would\N{\rChinese}作为狩猎采集者，你会认为他们会
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.66,0:26:50.50,English,,0,0,0,,discard the dwarf, kill the dwarf, or maybe\N{\rChinese}抛弃矮人，杀死矮人，或者可能
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.26,0:26:52.94,English,,0,0,0,,leave the dwarf. Leave the dwarf behind, okay?\N{\rChinese}离开矮人。离开矮人，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.26,0:26:59.62,English,,0,0,0,,But from DNA analysis, what we know is this.\N{\rChinese}但从DNA分析来看，我们知道的是这样。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.92,0:27:02.28,English,,0,0,0,,This skeleton,\N{\rChinese}这具骨架，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.68,0:27:07.02,English,,0,0,0,,okay, this person had the same amount of food,\N{\rChinese}好的，这个人拥有与其他人相同的食物量，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.20,0:27:09.66,English,,0,0,0,,the same quality of food as everyone else.\N{\rChinese}食物质量也与其他人相同。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.62,0:27:12.80,English,,0,0,0,,Meaning that even though\N{\rChinese}也就是说，虽然
