Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.46,0:27:30.66,English,,0,0,0,,And at the end of this person's life,\N{\rChinese}在此人一生结束时，
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.86,0:27:35.98,English,,0,0,0,,he was granted a elaborate burial,\N{\rChinese}他被安排了隆重的葬礼。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.20,0:27:40.46,English,,0,0,0,,okay? And we know this from the archeological research, yeah?\N{\rChinese}好的？我们从考古研究里知道这点，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.56,0:27:43.86,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay. Okay, does that make sense, guys?\N{\rChinese}好的，明白。这样说通吗，大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.14,0:27:47.00,English,,0,0,0,,All right, so let me ask you this question.\N{\rChinese}好的，那我来问你们一个问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.14,0:27:52.00,English,,0,0,0,,Let's make the assumption that he was, in fact, a dwarf.\N{\rChinese}假设他确实是个矮人。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.00,0:27:54.36,English,,0,0,0,,And that he was, in fact, contributing to the community.\N{\rChinese}并且他确实为社区做出了贡献。
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.80,0:27:57.96,English,,0,0,0,,How could he contribute to the community?\N{\rChinese}他是如何为社区贡献的？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.76,0:28:04.06,English,,0,0,0,,How? They clearly thought he was special,\N{\rChinese}怎么？他们明显认为他很特别，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.30,0:28:05.76,English,,0,0,0,,but what made him special?\N{\rChinese}但是什么让他特别？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.92,0:28:11.22,English,,0,0,0,,If you're a dwarf,\N{\rChinese}如果你是个矮人，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.58,0:28:13.72,English,,0,0,0,,you can't hunt, what can you do?\N{\rChinese}你能干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.76,0:28:18.98,English,,0,0,0,,To me?.\N{\rChinese}对我来说呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.24,0:28:24.02,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, but\N{\rChinese}好的，好的，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.02,0:28:26.06,English,,0,0,0,,what else can you do besides food?\N{\rChinese}还有什么能做的？除了吃饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.30,0:28:32.48,English,,0,0,0,,Why would they think he was a special person?\N{\rChinese}他们为什么会认为他是个特殊的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.78,0:28:35.00,English,,0,0,0,,What could he do that others couldn't do?\N{\rChinese}他能做什么别人做不到的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.22,0:28:38.62,English,,0,0,0,,Yeah?.\N{\rChinese}是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.64,0:28:42.88,English,,0,0,0,,Thank you, okay.\N{\rChinese}谢谢，好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.10,0:28:48.52,English,,0,0,0,,So maybe the religion back then is that everyone is special.\N{\rChinese}所以那时的宗教可能就是人人都很特别。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.52,0:28:51.46,English,,0,0,0,,Everyone's the same, right? So if you're different,\N{\rChinese}每个人都一样，对吧？所以如果你不同，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.80,0:28:55.08,English,,0,0,0,,it doesn't mean you're less special,\N{\rChinese}这并不意味着你不够特别，
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.14,0:28:56.98,English,,0,0,0,,it means you're more special.\N{\rChinese}而是你更特别。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.34,0:29:02.12,English,,0,0,0,,It means that the mother goddess has given you a special power.\N{\rChinese}它意味着母神已赐予你一份特殊力量。
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:07.58,English,,0,0,0,,And maybe this power is to communicate with the spirit world, okay?\N{\rChinese}也许这份力量是与灵界沟通，行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.88,0:29:11.10,English,,0,0,0,,So maybe the cave paintings, as you say,\N{\rChinese}于是，正如你所说，洞穴壁画……
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.24,0:29:12.74,English,,0,0,0,,were done by people like this,\N{\rChinese}由像这样的人完成的，
